    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ancient Greek two-handled cups shaped like a woman's breast. The shape is principally known in black-figure and white-ground. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
